name: how much does it cost to die?
description: this is a simple cave, made with little money, but it is possible to see a great influence of the modernist architecture of death, very popular after the 20th century, few ornaments, little verticality. but surely someone who was much loved still lives around, because this tomb is perpetual, made with more than 3000 images through the technique of photogrammetry - 2021 Higor Casagrande
